three Americans being
held by the North.

08:04.133 --> 08:09.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
President Trump's America-first
policy means that human
rights will not determine U.S.

08:10.233 --> 08:12.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
relations with
foreign governments.

08:12.200 --> 08:16.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Secretary of State Rex
Tillerson took that message
to his employees today.

08:16.633 --> 08:21.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He said that, in some cases
-- quote -- "If you condition
our national security efforts

08:21.466 --> 08:26.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
on someone adopting
our values, it really
does create obstacles."

08:28.400 --> 08:31.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
President Trump hosted
Palestinian leader
Mahmoud Abbas today,
and vowed to try to make

08:31.533 --> 08:33.600 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
