chance of getting a peace deal.

08:40.666 --> 08:45.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
DONALD TRUMP, President
of the United States:
It's a -- something that
I think is, frankly,

08:47.066 --> 08:48.966 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
maybe not as difficult as people
have thought over the years.

08:48.966 --> 08:51.333 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
But we need two willing parties.

08:51.333 --> 08:53.433 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We believe Israel is willing.

08:53.433 --> 08:54.966 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We believe you're willing.

08:54.966 --> 08:57.200 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And if you both are willing,
we're going to make a deal.

08:57.200 --> 09:01.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The president
met with the Israeli prime
minister, Benjamin Netanyahu,

09:01.333 --> 09:03.433 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in February.

