around now to this new version.

11:02.066 --> 11:03.066 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Why?

11:03.066 --> 11:04.733 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

11:04.733 --> 11:09.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
MARK SANFORD (R),
South Carolina: It, in
essence, split things.

11:11.033 --> 11:14.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It left open the possibility
of federalism, which is to
say, we have historically had

11:14.500 --> 11:17.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
