states and different remedies.

11:17.800 --> 11:22.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Our founding fathers were so
intent on this idea of letting
states try different things

11:22.500 --> 11:26.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that they built it in, though we
had a population of about four
million people when our country

11:26.233 --> 11:28.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
started.

11:28.300 --> 11:31.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, I think what it does is,
it allows Vermont to go to a
single-payer system if Vermont

11:31.733 --> 11:35.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
