Carolina can go to a more
market-based system, if it chose

11:35.733 --> 11:37.766 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to do so.

11:37.766 --> 11:40.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, you know,
I'm sure, that today Congressman
Fred Upton and others worked

11:40.800 --> 11:45.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
on an amendment, a proposal to
further change this new version
that would add more money

11:47.733 --> 11:52.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
to cover those
people with so-called
preexisting conditions.

11:52.633 --> 11:57.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Are you confident, from what
you know, though, that this is
going to guarantee everybody

11:57.300 --> 11:59.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
