conditions coverage?

11:59.500 --> 12:01.666 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

12:01.666 --> 12:03.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARK SANFORD: Built into the
base bill is this issue of
guarantee issue, so that you

12:03.166 --> 12:07.466 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
