this bill does allow,
what happens to them?

12:17.566 --> 12:22.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And that's why it's
been important that this
issue of a risk pool,
as Maine has done, was

12:23.300 --> 12:25.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
built into the bill.

12:25.266 --> 12:27.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
