other folks' insistence, that
a little bit more money be

12:37.333 --> 12:39.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
built in as a cushion
on this front.

12:39.466 --> 12:44.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
