is still going to leave too

13:34.333 --> 13:35.533 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
many people out.

13:35.533 --> 13:37.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So, they can't
support it either.

13:37.233 --> 13:38.900 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

13:38.900 --> 13:40.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
MARK SANFORD: Well, one,
I would expect them to
say that as advocates.

13:40.833 --> 13:43.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And that is what
they're supposed to do.

13:43.333 --> 13:48.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think that what we're
trying to include is that vast
unspoken group out there that

13:48.166 --> 13:52.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
