by about 30 percent.

14:02.600 --> 14:07.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so what we're trying to do
is to let insurance be insurance
for the preponderance of folks

14:09.500 --> 14:12.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
