marketplace that have seen their
premiums rise dramatically,

14:12.533 --> 14:17.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
while, at the same time,
covering folks that indeed have
a preexisting condition or have

14:19.366 --> 14:22.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
been -- seen the consequence
of a horrendous accident.

14:22.800 --> 14:24.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And I think that that's
what this bill does.

14:24.400 --> 14:26.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It tries to cover both.

14:26.433 --> 14:29.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
