of this House at this
particular moment in time.

14:32.566 --> 14:35.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You are saying
it does so imperfectly.

14:35.066 --> 14:39.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The doubters out there
