15:45.800 --> 15:50.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
on in this House, even that
happens, this is a debate that
is going to be ongoing, because

15:52.733 --> 15:55.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think that that tension
between security and freedom is
one that fits in this debate,

15:55.933 --> 15:58.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
