20:35.100 --> 20:40.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The White House and Speaker Ryan
have really been twisting arms.

20:41.600 --> 20:43.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's what I'm hearing from my
colleagues here in the Capitol.

20:43.600 --> 20:47.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But we have the American people
on our side, in addition to
America's doctors, nurses,

20:48.366 --> 20:49.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
so many advocates.

20:49.600 --> 20:52.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
