52:50.700 --> 52:53.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And the first step is to
first understand the storm.

52:53.033 --> 52:57.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You can't forecast a storm until
you understand it, and we're
just getting to the point where

52:57.166 --> 53:02.166 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
